title: Easy Spiced Pork & Roasted Pumpkin with Cucumber Salad & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: We've elevated this classic dish by giving our succulent pork steaks a coat of our tasty seasoning – straight from Nan's pantry –then topping them off with a mouth-watering creamy pesto dressing. And the trick to making these pumpkin wedges delicious? Roasting them with honey until golden and tender.

